{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1686-02a_024","@resp":"wordpro","head":{"value":"Le Poëte rebuté. Caprice","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", février 1686 (première partie) [tome 2], p. 24-31","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":[{},"Le talent de sçavoir faire des Vers, est un talent qui a son merite, mais il est infructueux, &amp; la pluspart de ceux qui s’en mêlent, ne sont pas trop bien avec la fortune. C’est ce qui a fait faire l’Ouvrage qui suit à un galant homme, qui n’a trouvé que de vains amusemens dans le commerce des Muses."],"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"#":{"value":"LE POËTE REBUTÉ.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#"},"lb":{},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"CAPRICE.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/hi/#"}}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’abandonne le Parnasse,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et pour ne vous point tromper,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Muses, je cede ma place","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A qui voudra l’occuper ;","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"I’ay plus tiré de ma Veine","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que je n’avois esperé,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et les eaux de l’Hypocrene","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"M’ont enfin desalteré.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[7]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Vois-je dés que je frequente","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ce froid &amp; maigre costeau,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que son pasquerage augmente","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’embonpoint de mon Troupeau ?","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dans la langueur qui l’accable","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je le vois prest à perir,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et nul aspect favorable","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne s’offre à le secourir.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[7]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Qu’ay-je à faire des conquestes","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des Heros &amp; des Guerriers,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Si quand j’en chante les Festes,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je seche aux pieds des Lauriers ?","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Oüy, Muses, je le veux croire,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La gloire est vostre destin,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais qui ne vit que de gloire,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Peut fort bien mourir de faim.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[7]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" En vain j’ay fait mon possible","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour mettre en credit ma voix,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mon Creancier inflexible","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La voudroit d’or &amp; de poids ;","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De mes plus douces paroles","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il prend le sens de travers,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il veut de bonnes pistoles,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et n’a que faire de Vers.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[7]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Enfin dans vos champs steriles,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Muses, on a beau semer,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ie voy que les plus habiles","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Rarement les font germer.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Leur sort ne fait point d’envie,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Car la pluspart seurement,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne chantent toute leur vie","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que pour mourir pauvrement.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[7]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[10]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Que pourrois-je donc pretendre,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Moy, dont les foibles concerts","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ont peine à se faire entendre","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aux Echos les plus ouverts ?","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Aux doux sons de vostre Lire","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quand ma voix pourroit fournir,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui s’avisera de dire","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’il la faudroit soûtenir ?","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[7]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[12]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Lors qu’une ardeur indiscrete","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"M’a conduit au champ de Mars,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"N’ay-je pas pris la trompete","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour suivre nos étendars ?","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quand LOUIS par ses Conquestes","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A tout pris, tout desolé,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En a-t-on fait quelques Festes","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont je ne me sois mêlé ?","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[7]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[14]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Ay-je manqué ny de zele,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ny de soins laborieux ?","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Infatigable, &amp; fidelle,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que pouvois-je faire mieux ?","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Par tout à perte d’haleine","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"J’ay secondé vos accords,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et n’ay tiré de ma Veine","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que d’inutiles transports.","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[7]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[16]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Sonnets, Madrigaux, Devises,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Poëmes, Odes, Chansons,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’à tant &amp; tant de reprises","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"I’ay tourné de cent façons ;","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Rimes riches &amp; parfaites,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que m’avez-vous épargné ?","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@r